<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main/styles.css">
    <title>Blog Website</title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <section id="header">
        <div></div>
        <div id="header-menu">
            <a href="#">
                <img src="main/images/svgs/house-user-solid.svg" alt="">
            </a>
            <a href="">About</a>
            <a href="">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <div id="user-login">
            <button>
                <img src="main/images/svgs/user-solid.svg" alt="">
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Blog Container -->
    <section id="blog-container">
        <!-- Left side menu -->
        <section id="menu-bar">
            <h2>Menu Bar</h2>
            <a href="">Feed</a>
            <a href="">Messages</a>
            <a href="">Friends</a>
            <a href="">Activity</a>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Post Feed -->
        <section id="feed">
            <h1>Welcome Home</h1>
            <small>The only way through is forward...</small>

            <div>
                <div id="post-data">
                    <a href="">
                        <img src="main/images/svgs/user-regular.svg" alt="User Icon">
                    </a>
                    <span class="username">colorful_clove</span>
                    <small class="time-stamp">05.18.24 9:24PM</small>
                </div>
                <div id="post-message">
                    Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Perferendis ab veniam fuga, rerum culpa aliquid ad et sapiente. Tenetur aut odit quam vero temporibus sed rem itaque. Quidem, animi quam!
                    At illum soluta consequuntur nisi error rem quod consectetur laborum eaque culpa recusandae ab doloremque, ducimus blanditiis minus ratione enim quibusdam! Provident obcaecati voluptate maxime quae quaerat illum nobis consequatur.
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Post Form Menu -->
        <section id="post-bar">
            <h2>What's On Your Mind?</h2>
            <form action="/update-feed" method="post">
                <input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Subject">
                <input type="text" name="message" placeholder="What do you want to say?">
                <input type="submit" value="Post">
            </form>
        </section>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <section id="footer"></section>
</body>
</html>